      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/y/71c47a/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2021-02-08T04:42:52.892Z",
      "cooked": "<p>First of all, congratulations on your application which perfectly meets my needs. It is simple and contains the essentials.<br>\nHowever here is a list of suggested improvements.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Be able to share activity to Garmin connect with mileage if possible. I\u2019m talking about the activity that is in History.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Choice of more or less loud sound</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>A final of the exercise more in apotheosis</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>FTP test which proposes which calculates the FTP at the end and proposes to update it in the user parameters</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>History, being able to delete / modify an activity. To be able to consult the history on the website.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ability to add speed, mileage on the training screen</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>To be able to launch a Spinning test of the home trainer</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>To be able to use the application in an outdoor bike without a power sensor and without a home trainer, with target heart rate.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Display the name of the workout on the training screen of the app to know which workout is in progress.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>",
